Package org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.objects.addressing

Class DestinationAddressContainer

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.objects.addressing.DestinationAddressContainer
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
@Immutable public class DestinationAddressContainer extends Object implements Serializable
A container for any type of destination network address (Topocast or Geocast). Since it has variables for both types, you should be careful about using getters because it can lead to NullPointerExceptions.
